redstone-helper.feature.hints.hint.1:
Tired of melting redstone dust?
 Maybe /autowire will help you
redstone-helper.feature.hints.hint.2:
You can use /bits to convert
numbers between BIT and HEX systems
redstone-helper.feature.hints.hint.3: You can use /macro to create macros commands
redstone-helper.feature.hints.hint.4: You can use /gamerule instantLampsTurnOff true to disable lamps delay
redstone-helper.feature.hints.hint.5: You can use /airplace to enable airplace
redstone-helper.feature.hints.hint.7:
Forgot how many items you need for a signal?
/calc-redstone-signal will help you!
redstone-helper.feature.hints.hint.8:
Always dreamed of placing blocks in the air?
Now it's possible with /airplace!
redstone-helper.feature.hints.hint.9:
Tired of repeaters?
Let /autowire do all the work for you
redstone-helper.feature.hints.hint.11:
Manipulate bits and hexadecimal numbers easily
with BIT Operations™
redstone-helper.feature.hints.hint.12:
Don't forget to check for mod updates
if version checking is disabled in ModMenu!
redstone-helper.feature.hints.hint.13:
The mod supports different languages! Want to add yours?
Translate it to Crowdin!
/redstone-helper crowdin
redstone-helper.feature.hints.hint.14:
Use ModMenu to customize
the appearance of the Redstone-Helper interface
redstone-helper.feature.hints.hint.15:
Don't forget about quick teleport with
/quicktp. Install it on a button for
even greater convenience!

Automatic placement of redstone?
Just type /autodust!

The Toast system will
always inform you of important information
right?

If you are tired of these hints,
just turn them off in the mod settings

Did you know that you can add
your own translation for Redstone Helper?
/redstone-helper crowdin

Beware of /clear-inventory!
She will clean even the most important items from chests!

Need to get somewhere fast?
Type /quicktp and you're done!
redstone-helper.feature.hints.hint.23:
Say no to delays - use
/gamerule instantLampsTurnOff true to turn off your lamps instantly!
